{"tid":1793639,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原班人馬開續集《宮心計3之攻心計》","createTime":"2019-12-22T14:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T14:10:37.000Z","uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa192c5d42227825bc230acc171fe8be9d00bb0d","tid":1793639,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:02:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足落得場，一定有聽過黑警呢句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">定啲來喎，手都震曬！</span></span><br />\n基於唔同人係唔同場合，都聽過呢句，所以，我肯定係有人教的。甚至乎，係一種戰術。而戰術呢樣樣，無話只有一方可以用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦白講，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">任何人聽到呢句，都會有啲怯。</span>而黑警嘅目的，就係想係心理上佔上風。（我廢，有冇心理學家手足可以補充兩句？）<br />\n<br />\n但必須強調，<br />\n鬥人多，我地先係上風；<br />\n鬥道理，我地都係上風。<br />\n而佢，真係窮得只剩一把槍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kta4rSD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkta4rSD.jpg&h=d3e6eaf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係好人，建議下次係呢類場面，大家一齊提一提佢：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定啲來喎，手都震曬！</span></span><br />\n（自己想像一下個場面。）<br />\n<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n真。攻心計"},{"pid":"e8538272e3edd51eb409f7ffe16090e1adf82eb1","tid":1793639,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}